'''安德魯·大衛·戴華亞'''（{{lang-en|'''Andrew David Driver'''}}，{{bd|1987年|11月20日|catidx=Driver, Andrew}}）出生於[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[大曼徹斯特郡|大曼徹斯特郡]]的[[奧爾德姆|奧爾德姆]]（Oldham），是一名[[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[中場#翼鋒|翼鋒]]。

==生平==
===球會===
戴華亞在奧爾德姆出生及成長，但於11歲時因父親工作的關係，舉家遷移到[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]][[愛丁堡|愛丁堡]]附近定居<small><ref name="England call">{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/heart_of_midlothian/8074641.stm |title=Driver 'delight' at England call |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-05-29 |accessdate=2009-05-30 |archive-date=2019-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190813162512/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/heart_of_midlothian/8074641.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。戴華亞開始時為赫捷臣維爾（Hutchison Vale AFC）參加足球比賽，其後於2003年加盟[[哈茨足球俱乐部|赫斯]]。

2006年戴華亞跟隨一隊到[[奧地利|奧地利]]展開季前[[熱身賽|熱身賽]]，在3場[[友誼賽|友誼賽]]中全數擔任正選，更交出4次助攻的好成績。8月戴華亞簽署五年延長合約，留隊直到2011年。[[2006年至2007年蘇格蘭足球超級聯賽|2006/07年球季]]戴華亞晉身一隊，8月26日主場4-1擊敗[[因弗内斯足球俱乐部|恩華尼斯]]，戴華亞在下半場76分鐘首次以後補身份上陣，入場後僅4分鐘更在窄角度將球射入球門網頂，將領先比數擴大到3-1<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/5284746.stm |title=Hearts 4-1 Inverness CT |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-08-26 |accessdate=2009-05-30 |archive-date=2020-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113151502/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/5284746.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；2007年4月29日戴華亞與赫斯到訪賽後舉行[[蘇超|蘇超]]冠軍頒獎禮的[[凯尔特人足球俱乐部|些路迪]]，大搞破壞以3-1取勝，戴華亞更在20[[碼|碼]]憑[[自由球|自由球]]「灣」入射成2-0<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/6598847.stm |title=Celtic 1-3 Hearts |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-04-29 |accessdate=2009-05-30 |archive-date=2019-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190916230658/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/6598847.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；5月12日戴華亞在「愛丁堡打吡」主場2-0擊敗[[希伯尼安足球俱乐部|喜百年]]再入一球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/6645245.stm |title=Hearts 2-0 Hibernian |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-05-12 |accessdate=2009-05-30 |archive-date=2019-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190811152120/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/6645245.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。戴華亞在首個球季上陣22場射入3球，但赫斯未能延續去季奪得聯賽亞軍的氣勢，僅取得第四位的成績，失落歐洲比賽的入場劵。

[[2007年至2008年蘇格蘭足球超級聯賽|2007/08年球季]]戴華亞開始成為常規正選，2007年8月18日主場1-1賽和升班馬[[格雷纳足球俱乐部|基特拿]]，半場入替的戴華亞「窩利」抽入先拔頭籌<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/6949195.stm |title=Hearts 1-1 Gretna |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-08-18 |accessdate=2009-05-30 |archive-date=2021-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303041850/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/6949195.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；9月15日正選上陣的戴華亞在主場對[[流浪者足球俱乐部|格拉斯哥流浪]]時再次妙射破網先開紀錄，協助球隊4-2獲勝<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/6988288.stm |title=Hearts 4-2 Rangers |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-09-15 |accessdate=2009-05-30 |archive-date=2021-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227021311/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/6988288.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；9月30日作客3-1擊敗[[圣米伦足球俱乐部|聖美倫]]，戴華亞再次先開紀錄<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/7017200.stm |title=St Mirren 1-3 Hearts |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-09-30 |accessdate=2009-05-30 |archive-date=2020-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017011328/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/7017200.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。連串精彩的演出及入球使戴華亞獲選為9月份「蘇超每月最佳青年球員」（Clydesdale Bank Young Player of the Month）<small><ref name="Awardee Driver"/></small>。本季戴化上陣29場及射入5球，但赫斯成績進一步下滑，未能晉身前六爭標組，只獲得第八位的排名。2008年8月29日戴華亞與赫斯延長合約五年，直到2013年才屆滿<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/heart_of_midlothian/7534134.stm |title=Driver signs Tynecastle extension |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-08-29 |accessdate=2009-05-30 |archive-date=2019-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190814031633/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/heart_of_midlothian/7534134.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

[[2008年至2009年蘇格蘭足球超級聯賽|2008/09年球季]]赫斯復甦，戴華亞合共上陣31場及射入5球，而赫斯亦取得季軍成績可以參加來年的[[2009/10賽季歐洲聯賽|歐霸盃足球聯賽]]外圍賽。

戴華亞的表現獲其他球會的賞識，據報包括[[基輔迪納摩足球俱樂部|基輔戴拿模]]、[[流浪者足球俱乐部|格拉斯哥流浪]]、[[埃弗顿足球俱乐部|愛華頓]]、[[博尔顿足球俱乐部|保頓]]及[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|般尼]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/heart_of_midlothian/7851506.stm |title=Laszlo urges Driver move caution |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-01-26 |accessdate=2009-05-30 |archive-date=2019-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190814154011/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/heart_of_midlothian/7851506.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，赫斯先後拒絕兩支[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]球會的出價，2008年夏季[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|般尼]]首先提出的50萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11781_3690989,00.html |title=Burnley fail in latest attempt to snap up Driver |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2008-06-14 |accessdate=2009-05-30 |archive-date=2016-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161105223301/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11781_3690989,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，其後增加到75萬英鎊<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/7467448.stm |title=Burnley could end Driver interest |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-06-21 |accessdate=2009-05-30 |archive-date=2019-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190819015056/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/7467448.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，而[[考文垂足球俱乐部|高雲地利]]在2009年1月轉會窗的100萬英鎊同樣被拒<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/heart_of_midlothian/7861534.stm |title=Coventry table £1m bid for Driver |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-01-30 |accessdate=2009-05-30 |archive-date=2019-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190816094912/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/heart_of_midlothian/7861534.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2009年6月7日[[英超|英超]]升班馬[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:伯恩利;zh-hk:般尼}-]]提出以150萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]，潛在可增加到200萬英鎊，收購戴華亞，惟赫斯認為這名新晉[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U21國腳]]價值約400至500萬英鎊，雙方繼續商討<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/heart_of_midlothian/8135884.stm |title=Burnley contact Hearts for Driver |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-06-07 |accessdate=2009-07-31 |archive-date=2019-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190811080752/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/heart_of_midlothian/8135884.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。戴華亞在7月27日於赫斯季前[[熱身賽|熱身賽]]對[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:南安普顿;zh-hk:修咸頓}-]]觸傷[[腳跟|腳跟]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/heart_of_midlothian/8171391.stm |title=Driver returns for scan on heel |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-07-27 |accessdate=2009-07-31 |archive-date=2019-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190811172155/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/heart_of_midlothian/8171391.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，需要養傷6星期而缺席季初的比賽<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/heart_of_midlothian/8176063.stm |title=Hearts suffer Driver injury blow |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-07-30 |accessdate=2009-07-31 |archive-date=2019-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190811172249/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/heart_of_midlothian/8176063.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

===國家隊===
戴華亞曾代表蘇格蘭學童隊參加國際比賽，並在對英格蘭時取得入球<small><ref name="England call"/></small>。但由於[[英國|英國]]四個[[構成國家|構成國家]]有協議，只可選派有[[血親|血親]]關係的球員代表參賽，所以戴華亞無緣代表[[蘇格蘭足球代表隊|蘇格蘭]]上陣<small><ref name="Awardee Driver">{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/heart_of_midlothian/7044285.stm |title=Awardee Driver misses Scots caps |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-10-14 |accessdate=2009-05-30 |archive-date=2019-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190816210154/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/heart_of_midlothian/7044285.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。[[蘇格蘭足球總會|蘇格蘭足球總會]]建議放寬限制，容許曾在當地就讀五年或以上的球員可以參賽，並獲得[[威爾斯足球總會|威爾斯]]及[[北愛爾蘭足球協會|北愛爾蘭]]的支持，於2008/09年球季結束後呈請[[國際足協|國際足協]]批准<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7917910.stm |title=Scots seek change on eligibility |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-03-01 |accessdate=2009-05-30 |archive-date=2020-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923091632/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7917910.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，戴化表示希望為蘇格蘭效力<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/heart_of_midlothian/7931282.stm |title=Driver wants to play for Scotland |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-03-08 |accessdate=2009-05-30 |archive-date=2021-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227111243/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/heart_of_midlothian/7931282.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。[[英格蘭足球總會|英格蘭足球總會]]雖然同意，但卻在議案尚未審批前，「偷步」挑選戴華亞加入2009年6月在[[瑞典|瑞典]]舉行[[2009年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽|2009年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽]]決賽週，[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U-21]]初選參賽名單，此舉使到蘇格蘭足球總會感到非常失望<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/heart_of_midlothian/8052787.stm |title=Driver set for England U21 call |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-05-15 |accessdate=2009-05-30 |archive-date=2019-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190815123642/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/heart_of_midlothian/8052787.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。主教練[[斯图尔特·皮尔斯|皮雅斯]]在5月底宣佈決選名單，戴華亞獲選成為其中一員<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8070858.stm |title=Walcott named in U21 Euro squad |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-05-27 |accessdate=2009-05-30 |archive-date=2009-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090601165338/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8070858.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，皮雅斯表示因[[阿伦·伦农|艾朗·連儂]]受傷而挑選戴化作為替補，而戴華亞亦樂於代表英格蘭參賽<small><ref name="England call"/></small>。6月22日首次扳甲上陣，在U21歐錦賽最後一場分組賽對[[德國21歲以下國家足球隊|德國U21]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8111533.stm |title=England U21 1-1 Germany U21 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-06-22 |accessdate=2009-06-23 |archive-date=2020-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200802204857/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8111533.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

